<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="sb;5;7562" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB5,7562</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Μάξιμος Χαιρήμονι καὶ 

    <lb n="2"/>Εὐδαίμονι τοῖς <expan>γλυκυτάτ<ex cert="high">οις</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="3"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="4"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πρὸ μ</supplied>ὲν πάντων εὔχο-

    <lb n="5"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μαι ὑ</supplied>μᾶς ὑγιαίνειν. 

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γινώσκ</supplied>ειν</corr><sic><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γινωσ</supplied>κιν</sic></choice> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δ</supplied>ὲ <choice><corr>ὑμᾶς</corr><sic>ημας</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="7"/>θέλ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ω</supplied> ὅτι θεῶν σωσάν-

    <lb n="8"/>των <choice><corr>ἐγενόμην</corr><sic>εγεναμην</sic></choice> εἰς τὴν 

    <lb n="9"/>πόλιν τῇ <num value="17">ιζ</num>, καὶ ὁ ἡγεμὼν 

    <lb n="10"/><choice><corr>ἐγένετο</corr><sic>εγενατο</sic></choice> ἐν τῇ <choice><corr>πόλει</corr><sic>πολι</sic></choice> τῇ <num value="16">ιϛ</num>, 

    <lb n="11"/>Τίτος Φούριος Οὐικτω-

    <lb n="12"/>ρῖνος.  ἐρωτηθέντες, 

    <lb n="13"/>ὡς καὶ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κα</supplied>τ᾽ ὄψιν ὑμᾶς 

    <lb n="14"/>ἠρώτησα, ἀνέχεσθαι ἀλ-

    <lb n="15"/>λήλων καὶ φιλεῖν ἑ-

    <lb n="16"/>αυτούς, <choice><corr>ἀναγκαίως</corr><sic>ανανκαιως</sic></choice> καὶ 

    <lb n="17"/>νῦν γράφω· μελησάτω 

    <lb n="18"/>ὑμῖν καὶ περὶ Θερμου-

    <lb n="19"/>θαρίου, ἵνα ἐλθὼν ἀνθο-

    <lb n="20"/>μολογηθῇ μοι περὶ 

    <lb n="21"/>τῆς εὐστ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θ</unclear>είας ὑμῶν. 

    <lb n="22"/>περὶ τῶν ἔργων τοῦ 

    <lb n="23"/>ἀμπελῶνος, ὡς ἐνε-

    <lb n="24"/>τειλάμην <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>υμειν</sic></choice>, μὴ 

    <lb n="25"/>ἀμελήσητε, καθὸ δύ-

    <lb n="26"/>ναμις ὑμῖν ἐστιν· 

    <lb n="27"/>καὶ μὴ <choice><corr>παραβουλεύεσθαι</corr><sic>παραβολευεσθαι</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="28"/>εἴ τι δὲ ἐὰν πράξω, εὐθέ-

    <lb n="29"/>ως <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>υμειν</sic></choice> δηλώσω. 

    <lb n="30"/>ξενίζομαι δὲ ἐγὼ καὶ 

    <lb n="31"/>ὁ σὺν ἐμοὶ πλεύσας Σαρα-

    <lb n="32"/>πίων υἱὸς Δημητρίου 

    <lb n="33"/>υἱοῦ Ἀπελεκήτου εἰς 

    <lb n="34"/>τὴν ῥύμην Ὠριγένους 

    <lb n="35"/>ἐν οἰκίᾳ Ἡρακλείδου τοῦ 

    <lb n="36"/><sic>του</sic> Καλαῆ. 

    <lb n="37"/>ἐρρῶσθαι ὑμᾶς εὔχομαι. 

    <lb n="38"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="22">κβ</num>, Ἐπεὶφ <num value="20">κ</num>. 

    <lb n="39"/>ἐάν μοι γράφητε, δηλώσα-

    <lb n="40"/>τέ μοι καὶ περὶ Ἁροῦτος τῆς 

    <lb n="41"/>μικρᾶς πῶς περιέχει. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="42"/><expan>ἀπόδο<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> ἐν <expan>Ναρμού<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θ</unclear><ex cert="high">ει</ex></expan> <g type="x"/> παρὰ <choice><corr>Μαξίμου</corr><sic>μαξιμον</sic></choice> <choice><corr>γραμματέως</corr><sic>γραμματεα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="43"/>γερδίων </ab></div></div><div n="meta.17409" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.17409" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="159" notBefore="159" type="textDate" value="0159-07-14">14. Juli 159</date></p></div><div n="meta.17409" part="N" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 10: <date type="mentioned" value="0159-07-10">10. Juli 159</date></p><p>Z. 9: <date type="mentioned" value="0159-07-11">11. Juli 159</date></p></div><div n="meta.17409" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">PSI</title><biblScope type="volume">12</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1241</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">17409</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0238</series>; <biblScope type="volume">12</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1241</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0238;12;1241" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.17409" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">408/409</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.17409" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.17409" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">SB V 7562</bibl></div><div n="meta.17409" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Alexandria</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>